*Opasan* kriminalac je uhapšen. (A dangerous criminal was arrested.)
Deca su svesna da je *opasno* sa njima igrati se prilikom saobraćajnih ulica. (The children are aware that it is dangerous to play with them in the vicinity of traffic streets.)
U poslednje vreme, *opasni* virusi su postali česta pojava. (Lately, dangerous viruses have become a common occurrence.)
Oni su ubili *opasnog* zvera. (They killed a dangerous beast.)
Prepoznali su *opasnu* situaciju i pobegli. (They recognized the dangerous situation and ran away.)